nt||cp|8|AT|^B@2^Y@3^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|Wow, I think Azin is a ringer. Excellent play of the cards. Moe should take the Ace of hearts and play a diamond earlier. Then he can only make 4 because Azin cannot afford to play spades. I have noticed that many students duck Aces, sometimes unnecessarily.|
